Dan Haiek and Armchair Analyst Matt Doyle preview the Western Conference clash between the Vancouver Whitecaps and Colorado Rapids. Will the Rapids shut down Pedro Morales? Can Colorado finally score from the run of play? Find out Saturday at 630pm ET on MLS Live.
